OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry but cloudy morning, low
OL,6,Fcloud and some misty patches possible
OL,7,Fin the east with brighter spells
OL,8,Fpossible in the west. Cloud breaking
OL,9,Fup from late morning to give long
OL,10,Fsunny spells in the afternoon. Light
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry evening with late
OL,14,Fsunshine, then long clear spells after
OL,15,Fsunset. Long clear spells overnight,
OL,16,Fbut a few mist and fog patches
OL,17,Fpossibly forming, especially in the
OL,18,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
